                     <interp inst="t17721209-83-person709" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I heard the cry, stop thief! I saw the prisoner running, and Mr. Warner and Mr. Black following him; I joined in their pursuit and he was never out of my sight till the mob got round him and he was taken.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence.</p>
               <p>I was walking with a friend from Norton Falgate; I was stopt by these people as I was crossing Cow-lane; for why I cannot tell.</p>
               <p>He called three witnesses, who gave him a good character.</p>
